Hmm 
Well, Shani Arshad did composed music so well, but the Question is, is there was any mistake in the presentation???
So, from Me, yes! As other critics thinks, 
1st the part of Sara Haider wasn't so strong, I mean to say Shani couldn't composed her portion very well, that wasn't solid as well as that was quite boring also.
And 2nd the song suddenly ended the "end" of song also not good, it was looking that song is still continue but actually the song was ended suddenly.
So, that's why I also have seen so many negative comments for Shani Arshad.
